hh3cIPSecMonitor.name: hh3cIPSecMonitor
hh3cIPSecMonitor.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cIPSecMonitor.description: The MIB is designed to get statistic information of IPSec tunnels. With this MIB, we can get information of a certain tunnel or all tunnels.

Hh3cDiffHellmanGrp.name: Hh3cDiffHellmanGrp
Hh3cDiffHellmanGrp.description: The Diffie Hellman Group used in the IKE and IPSec negotiations. invalidGroup(2147483647) is defined as invalid value.

Hh3cEncapMode.name: Hh3cEncapMode
Hh3cEncapMode.description: The encapsulation mode used by an IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel. invalidMode(2147483647) is defined as invalid value.

Hh3cEncryptAlgo.name: Hh3cEncryptAlgo
Hh3cEncryptAlgo.description: The encryption algorithm used in the IKE and IPSec negotiations. invalidAlg(2147483647) is defined as invalid value.

Hh3cAuthAlgo.name: Hh3cAuthAlgo
Hh3cAuthAlgo.description: The authentication algorithm used in the IKE negotiations. invalidAlg(2147483647) is defined as invalid value.

Hh3cTrapStatus.name: Hh3cTrapStatus
Hh3cTrapStatus.description: The switch which determines whether send a trap or not.

Hh3cTrafficType.name: Hh3cTrafficType
Hh3cTrafficType.description: The type of the data flow.

Hh3cIPSecNegoType.name: Hh3cIPSecNegoType
Hh3cIPSecNegoType.description: The type of key used by an IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel. invalidType(2147483647) is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunnelTable.name: hh3cIPSecTunnelTable
hh3cIPSecTunnelTable.description: The IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel Table. There is one entry in this table for each active IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunIfIndex.name: hh3cIPSecTunIfIndex
hh3cIPSecTunIfIndex.description: The interface index( the ifIndex of ifTable ).

hh3cIPSecTunEntryIndex.name: hh3cIPSecTunEntryIndex
hh3cIPSecTunEntryIndex.description: The index of IPSec policy applied in the interface.

hh3cIPSecTunIndex.name: hh3cIPSecTunIndex
hh3cIPSecTunIndex.description: The index of IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel Table. The value of the index is a number which begins at one and is incremented with each tunnel that is created. The value of this object will wrap at 2,147,483,647.

hh3cIPSecTunIKETunnelIndex.name: hh3cIPSecTunIKETunnelIndex
hh3cIPSecTunIKETunnelIndex.description: The index of the associated IPSec Phase-1 IKE Tunnel (IKETunIndex in the IKETunnelTable). 2147483647 is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunLocalAddr.name: hh3cIPSecTunLocalAddr
hh3cIPSecTunLocalAddr.description: The IP address of the local peer for the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel. 0.0.0.0 is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunRemoteAddr.name: hh3cIPSecTunRemoteAddr
hh3cIPSecTunRemoteAddr.description: The IP address of the remote peer for the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel. 0.0.0.0 is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunKeyType.name: hh3cIPSecTunKeyType
hh3cIPSecTunKeyType.description: The key negotiate mode used by the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunEncapMode.name: hh3cIPSecTunEncapMode
hh3cIPSecTunEncapMode.description: The encapsulation mode used by the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInitiator.name: hh3cIPSecTunInitiator
hh3cIPSecTunInitiator.description: The initiator of this IPSec tunnel. Value none is used for manual IPsec tunnel, for there is no initiator or responder in this method.

hh3cIPSecTunLifeSize.name: hh3cIPSecTunLifeSize
hh3cIPSecTunLifeSize.description: The negotiated LifeSize of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel in kilobytes. 0 is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunLifeTime.name: hh3cIPSecTunLifeTime
hh3cIPSecTunLifeTime.description: The negotiated LifeTime of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel in seconds. 2147483647 is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunRemainTime.name: hh3cIPSecTunRemainTime
hh3cIPSecTunRemainTime.description: The remain time of SA in seconds. 2147483647 is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunActiveTime.name: hh3cIPSecTunActiveTime
hh3cIPSecTunActiveTime.description: The duration the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel has been active in hundredths of seconds. 2147483647 is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunRemainSize.name: hh3cIPSecTunRemainSize
hh3cIPSecTunRemainSize.description: The remain LifeSize of SA in kilobytes. 0 is defined as invalid value.

hh3cIPSecTunTotalRefreshes.name: hh3cIPSecTunTotalRefreshes
hh3cIPSecTunTotalRefreshes.description: The total number of security association refreshing performed.

hh3cIPSecTunCurrentSaInstances.name: hh3cIPSecTunCurrentSaInstances
hh3cIPSecTunCurrentSaInstances.description: The number of security associations which are currently active or expiring.

hh3cIPSecTunInSaEncryptAlgo.name: hh3cIPSecTunInSaEncryptAlgo
hh3cIPSecTunInSaEncryptAlgo.description: The encryption algorithm used by the inbound security association of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInSaAhAuthAlgo.name: hh3cIPSecTunInSaAhAuthAlgo
hh3cIPSecTunInSaAhAuthAlgo.description: The authentication algorithm used by the inbound authentication header (AH) security association of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInSaEspAuthAlgo.name: hh3cIPSecTunInSaEspAuthAlgo
hh3cIPSecTunInSaEspAuthAlgo.description: The authentication algorithm used by the inbound encapsulation security protocol(ESP) security association of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunDiffHellmanGrp.name: hh3cIPSecTunDiffHellmanGrp
hh3cIPSecTunDiffHellmanGrp.description: The Diffie Hellman Group used by the security association of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunOutSaEncryptAlgo.name: hh3cIPSecTunOutSaEncryptAlgo
hh3cIPSecTunOutSaEncryptAlgo.description: The encryption algorithm used by the outbound security association of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunOutSaAhAuthAlgo.name: hh3cIPSecTunOutSaAhAuthAlgo
hh3cIPSecTunOutSaAhAuthAlgo.description: The authentication algorithm used by the outbound authentication header (AH) security association of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunOutSaEspAuthAlgo.name: hh3cIPSecTunOutSaEspAuthAlgo
hh3cIPSecTunOutSaEspAuthAlgo.description: The authentication algorithm used by the outbound encapsulation security protocol(ESP) security association of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunPolicyName.name: hh3cIPSecTunPolicyName
hh3cIPSecTunPolicyName.description: The policy name used by this IPSec tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunPolicyNum.name: hh3cIPSecTunPolicyNum
hh3cIPSecTunPolicyNum.description: The sequence number of policy used by this IPSec tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunStatus.name: hh3cIPSecTunStatus
hh3cIPSecTunStatus.description: The status of the IPSec Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunnelStatTable.name: hh3cIPSecTunnelStatTable
hh3cIPSecTunnelStatTable.description: The IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel Statistics Table.

hh3cIPSecTunInOctets.name: hh3cIPSecTunInOctets
hh3cIPSecTunInOctets.description: The total number of octets received by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel. This value is accumulated BEFORE determining whether or not the packet should be decompressed.

hh3cIPSecTunInDecompOctets.name: hh3cIPSecTunInDecompOctets
hh3cIPSecTunInDecompOctets.description: The total number of decompressed octets received by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel. This value is accumulated AFTER the packet is decompressed.

hh3cIPSecTunInPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunInPkts
hh3cIPSecTunInPkts.description: The total number of packets received by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunInDropPkts
hh3cIPSecTunInDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped during receiving process by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInReplayDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunInReplayDropPkts
hh3cIPSecTunInReplayDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped during receiving process due to Anti-Replay process by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInAuthFails.name: hh3cIPSecTunInAuthFails
hh3cIPSecTunInAuthFails.description: The total number of inbound authentication's which ended in failure by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInDecryptFails.name: hh3cIPSecTunInDecryptFails
hh3cIPSecTunInDecryptFails.description: The total number of inbound decryption's which ended in failure by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunOutOctets.name: hh3cIPSecTunOutOctets
hh3cIPSecTunOutOctets.description: The total number of octets sent by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel. This value is accumulated AFTER determining whether or not the packet should be compressed.

hh3cIPSecTunOutUncompOctets.name: hh3cIPSecTunOutUncompOctets
hh3cIPSecTunOutUncompOctets.description: The total number of uncompressed octets sent by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.This value is accumulated BEFORE the packet is compressed.

hh3cIPSecTunOutPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunOutPkts
hh3cIPSecTunOutPkts.description: The total number of packets sent by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunOutDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunOutDropPkts
hh3cIPSecTunOutDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped during sending process by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunOutEncryptFails.name: hh3cIPSecTunOutEncryptFails
hh3cIPSecTunOutEncryptFails.description: The total number of outbound encryption's which ended in failure by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunNoMemoryDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunNoMemoryDropPkts
hh3cIPSecTunNoMemoryDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to no enough memory by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunQueueFullDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunQueueFullDropPkts
hh3cIPSecTunQueueFullDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to queue full by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInvalidLenDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunInvalidLenDropPkts
hh3cIPSecTunInvalidLenDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to invalid length packet by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunTooLongDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunTooLongDropPkts
hh3cIPSecTunTooLongDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to too long packet by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecTunInvalidSaDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecTunInvalidSaDropPkts
hh3cIPSecTunInvalidSaDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to invalid SA by this IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecSaTable.name: hh3cIPSecSaTable
hh3cIPSecSaTable.description: The IPSec Phase-2 Security Protection Index Table. This table contains an entry for each active and expiring security association.

hh3cIPSecSaIndex.name: hh3cIPSecSaIndex
hh3cIPSecSaIndex.description: The number of the Sa associated with the Phase-2 Tunnel Table. The value of this index is a number which begins at one and is incremented with each Sa associated with an IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel. The value of this object will wrap at 2,147,483,647.

hh3cIPSecSaProtocol.name: hh3cIPSecSaProtocol
hh3cIPSecSaProtocol.description: The security protocol of the SA.

hh3cIPSecSaEncryptAlgo.name: hh3cIPSecSaEncryptAlgo
hh3cIPSecSaEncryptAlgo.description: The encryption algorithm used by the security association of the IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel.

hh3cIPSecSaAuthAlgo.name: hh3cIPSecSaAuthAlgo
hh3cIPSecSaAuthAlgo.description: The authentication algorithm used by the SA.

hh3cIPSecTrafficTable.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficTable
hh3cIPSecTrafficTable.description: The IPSec Phase-2 Tunnel Traffic Table.

hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalType.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalType
hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalType.description: The type of local peer. Possible values are: a single IP address, or an IP address range, or an IP subnet.

hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalAddr1.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalAddr1
hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalAddr1.description: The first specification of local peer's IP address. If the local peer type is single IP address, then this is the value of the IP address. If the local peer type is IP subnet, then this is the value of the subnet. If the local peer type is IP address range, then this is the value of beginning IP address of the range.

hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalAddr2.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalAddr2
hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalAddr2.description: The second specification of local peer's IP address. If the local peer type is single IP address, then this is the value of the IP address. If the local peer type is IP subnet, then this is the value of the subnet mask. If the local peer type is IP address range, then this is the value of ending IP address of the range.

hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalProtocol.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalProtocol
hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalProtocol.description: The protocol number of the local peer's traffic.

hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalPort.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalPort
hh3cIPSecTrafficLocalPort.description: The port number of the local peer's traffic.

hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteType.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteType
hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteType.description: The type of remote peer. Possible values are: a single IP address, or an IP address range, or an IP subnet.

hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteAddr1.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteAddr1
hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteAddr1.description: The first specification of remote peer's IP address. If the remote peer type is single IP address, then this is the value of the IP address. If the remote peer type is IP subnet, then this is the value of the subnet. If the remote peer type is IP address range, then this is the value of beginning IP address of the range.

hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteAddr2.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteAddr2
hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteAddr2.description: Single IP address, then this is the value of the IP address. If the remote peer type is IP subnet, then this is the value of the subnet mask. If the remote peer type is IP address range, then this is the value of ending IP address of the range.

hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteProtocol.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteProtocol
hh3cIPSecTrafficRemoteProtocol.description: The protocol number of the remote peer's traffic.

hh3cIPSecTrafficRemotePort.name: hh3cIPSecTrafficRemotePort
hh3cIPSecTrafficRemotePort.description: The port number of the remote peer's traffic.

hh3cIPSecGlobalActiveTunnels.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalActiveTunnels
hh3cIPSecGlobalActiveTunnels.description: The total number of currently active IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalActiveSas.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalActiveSas
hh3cIPSecGlobalActiveSas.description: The total number of currently active or expiring IPSec Phase-2 SA.

hh3cIPSecGlobalInOctets.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalInOctets
hh3cIPSecGlobalInOctets.description: The total number of octets received by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels. This value is accumulated BEFORE determining whether or not the packet should be decompressed.

hh3cIPSecGlobalInDecompOctets.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalInDecompOctets
hh3cIPSecGlobalInDecompOctets.description: The total number of decompressed octets received by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels. This value is accumulated AFTER the packet is decompressed.

hh3cIPSecGlobalInPkts.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalInPkts
hh3cIPSecGlobalInPkts.description: The total number of packets received by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalInDrops.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalInDrops
hh3cIPSecGlobalInDrops.description: The total number of packets dropped during receiving process by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalInReplayDrops.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalInReplayDrops
hh3cIPSecGlobalInReplayDrops.description: The total number of packets dropped during receiving process due to Anti-Replay process by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalInAuthFails.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalInAuthFails

hh3cIPSecGlobalInDecryptFails.description: The total number of inbound decryption's which ended in failure by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalOutOctets.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalOutOctets
hh3cIPSecGlobalOutOctets.description: The total number of octets sent by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels. This value is accumulated AFTER determining whether or not the packet should be compressed.

hh3cIPSecGlobalOutUncompOctets.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalOutUncompOctets
hh3cIPSecGlobalOutUncompOctets.description: The total number of uncompressed octets sent by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels. This value is accumulated BEFORE the packet is compressed.

hh3cIPSecGlobalOutPkts.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalOutPkts
hh3cIPSecGlobalOutPkts.description: The total number of packets sent by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalOutDrops.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalOutDrops
hh3cIPSecGlobalOutDrops.description: The total number of packets dropped during sending process by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalOutEncryptFails.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalOutEncryptFails
hh3cIPSecGlobalOutEncryptFails.description: The total number of outbound encryption's which ended in failure by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalNoMemoryDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalNoMemoryDropPkts
hh3cIPSecGlobalNoMemoryDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to no enough memory by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalQueueFullDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalQueueFullDropPkts
hh3cIPSecGlobalQueueFullDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to queue full by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalInvalidLenDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalInvalidLenDropPkts
hh3cIPSecGlobalInvalidLenDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to invalid packet length by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalTooLongDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to too long packet by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.

hh3cIPSecGlobalInvalidSaDropPkts.name: hh3cIPSecGlobalInvalidSaDropPkts
hh3cIPSecGlobalInvalidSaDropPkts.description: The total number of packets dropped due to invalid SA by all current and previous IPSec Phase-2 Tunnels.
